carcassonne.model

Class RealEstate

  • java.lang.Object
    • carcassonne.model.RealEstate

  • public abstract class RealEstate
extends java.lang.Object
    RealEstate is a class that creates abstract objects from features of several tiles that are connected to each other. Represents Land, Roads, Castles and Cloisters from the rules of Carcassonne.
